h.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tassius>Tassius</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 72<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/3/01 12:09:29 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Magical Jewellry</span><hr size=1> Some guild members were asking about magical jewellry for their lower level characters the other day, though I must confess I can't remember exactly who needed what - WIS was one I do remember and perhaps some of our warriors would like extra STR items. As there are a few of us in the guild who suffer an addiciton to jewelcraft I thought I would start this thread so that people can put their needs down, also those who can cobble together some items could mention what help they can give.<br>
<br>
My own skill is only 107 at the moment, but feel confident I could combine up to electrum and jade - and I'm about to start on gold which delivers even better stats. If you're not quite sure what you need have a look at eq.castersrealm.com where you'll find some useful tables on stone and metal combinations.<br>
<br>
Gladriel Lumenaura <p>Tassius Vindenervis.<BR>
Bane of the Undead,<BR>
Servant of Victus,<BR>
Friend of the Weak.<BR>
<BR>
tassius@btinternet.com</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/ukegdawen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kegdawen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/3/01 4:09:27 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://oz.uc.edu/~wrendn/kegdawenface.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magical Jewellry</span><hr size=1> I hadn't ask anyone about it before, but since you asked, I could really use something to buff my strength.  I have a very high agility already, but what I REALLY lack is strength.  I am constantly getting encumbered and often end up foregoing looting so as not to have to get bogged down or having to leave often to go sell.  So any strength enhancing jewelry would be greatly appreciated.  I don't have much plat (probably about 20-30 plat total currently), but if you tell me what you need to make such a thing, I will try to collect it, if you would assemble the pieces. <p>Long Live Victus Fortis!
<br><br>
Your Humble Brother,
<br>
Kegdawen</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/usemdayen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Semdayen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 72<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/4/01 9:14:36 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magical Jewellry</span><hr size=1> Anything with +wis for me Gladriel.<br>
<br>
A ranger without a trueshot (or the wisdom to make one) is like a very bad Tank. <p>Semdayen Maa'Sankari<Br>Ranger of the 21st Season<Br>In the Service of Tunare<Br><Br>'I am not lost - this is the scenic route'
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/beverquestersofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tassius>Tassius</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 77<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/4/01 3:06:21 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magical Jewellry</span><hr size=1> Ummm......I dont remember posting this.<br>
