tassius@btinternet.com</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/ugladrielnorrath.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gladriel norrath</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/5/01 12:23:38 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magical Jewellry</span><hr size=1> ....Yes it does seem a little confusing Tassius, I don't remember posting a ding-a-ling 24 note either, but it's there <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
