<br>
Gladriel Lumenaura <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/ugumbrils.showPublicProfile?language=EN>gumbrils</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 85<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/5/01 3:03:18 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.fbe.unsw.edu.au/staff/graham.hannah/eq/resources/gumbrils60x60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Magical Jewellry</span><hr size=1> Curses, so its ALL my fault now is it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
