<br>
Sem - I have 2 rings for you each +2 WIS, I can also swop these for +3 items in a week or so.<br>
<br>
If these items aren't what you need please don't worry about it, I can easily sell them back to the vendor at cost. I didn't mention before, but I don't want payment for anything below Jasper stones and electrum, above that I would appreciate it if my costs were covered or the raw materials provided. I've managed to haul my skill level, kicking and screaming, up to 112 now - so can also make some useful vs. items with +5 on them.<br>
